					I started programming when I was 14 years old in high school.
					<strong
						>I have been working with computers for as long as I can remember.</strong
					>
				</p>
				<p
					class="dark:[&>strong]:text-red-200 [&>strong]:text-red-500 [&>strong]:font-semibold"
				>
					What I remember most about my computer is that it only <strong>
						2 GB of RAM and it lasted 13 years</strong
					>. Thirteen years of pure windows 7.
				</p>
				<p
					class="dark:[&>strong]:text-yellow-200 [&>strong]:text-yellow-500 [&>strong]:font-semibold"
